aott/analysis/call_graph/analyzer.runa
Call Graph Analysis Module for AOTT Runtime Optimization

This module provides comprehensive call graph analysis for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Reachability and connectivity analysis
- Strongly connected component detection
- Call frequency and hotness analysis
- Inlining candidate identification
- Dead code detection via unreachable nodes
- Call depth and stack usage analysis
- Function importance ranking
- Bottleneck identification
- Call pattern recognition
- Profile-guided analysis decisions
- Cross-tier optimization opportunities
- Polymorphic call site analysis
- Escape analysis integration
- Performance impact prediction
- Call graph metrics computation
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

